Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.78,0:42:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续啊 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.73,0:42:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续 不然给她吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.16,0:42:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.58,0:42:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就继续吃
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.64,0:42:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.32,0:42:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给她一根吧 怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.93,0:42:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你全都吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.40,0:42:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈真贪婪啊 一根都不给你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.53,0:42:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛睁开
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.74,0:42:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 还有的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.86,0:42:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.73,0:42:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.00,0:42:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好欣赏下你妈那副样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.45,0:42:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被鸡巴包围了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.45,0:42:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睁开
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.94,0:43:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边也有
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.89,0:43:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边还没舔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.88,0:43:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.67,0:43:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边儿也要
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.29,0:43:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快点儿就找你女儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.80,0:43:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去找你女儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.25,0:43:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.42,0:43:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.30,0:43:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都要舔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.68,0:44:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有种想射的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.87,0:44:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不插进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.08,0:44:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肏你女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.05,0:44:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.27,0:44:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让女儿也参加哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.03,0:44:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.46,0:44:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能你来了啊 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.59,0:44:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.59,0:44:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再里面一点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.21,0:44:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你妈在干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.95,0:44:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.57,0:44:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.44,0:44:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是做爱啊 说 在口交
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.91,0:44:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还需加强学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.33,0:44:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来才是做爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.95,0:44:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来还不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.70,0:44:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 你妈奶子够大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.69,0:44:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那对大奶
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.75,0:44:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要是浪费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.98,0:45:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.40,0:45:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借你奶子一用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.04,0:45:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意 就找你女儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.67,0:45:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.50,0:45:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要干什么呢 看好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.00,0:45:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎能夹得挺舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.13,0:45:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.71,0:45:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.69,0:45:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫奶夹鸡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.37,0:45:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘也会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.13,0:45:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.45,0:45:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在给你插进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.42,0:46:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,张开 让我插进去
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.52,0:46:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.94,0:46:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.43,0:46:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.61,0:46:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.76,0:46:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答 回答
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.86,0:46:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不回答的话 就让你也体验一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.36,0:46:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.05,0:46:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.41,0:46:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.39,0:46:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插进去了\N插进哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.68,0:46:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.95,0:46:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.95,0:46:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在骚屄里
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.29,0:46:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进进出出的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.69,0:46:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的好
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.29,0:46:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.50,0:47:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你女儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.12,0:47:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何 舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.43,0:47:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.01,0:47:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 听见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.93,0:47:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不告诉你女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.87,0:47:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈现在很兴奋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.40,0:47:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.99,0:47:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快告诉女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.00,0:47:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.60,0:47:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 听不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.65,0:47:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快开口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.40,0:47:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.40,0:47:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的时候看着女儿的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.28,0:47:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉女儿啊 “妈妈很兴奋”
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.16,0:47:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.01,0:47:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.16,0:47:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪是 “不要”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.40,0:47:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.48,0:47:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.26,0:48:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚好
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.85,0:48:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.85,0:48:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过瘾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.90,0:48:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.88,0:48:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.09,0:48:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把屁眼儿展示出来
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.80,0:48:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.14,0:48:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己张开
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.26,0:48:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用你两只手
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.79,0:48:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.42,0:48:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快求我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.33,0:48:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.64,0:48:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插进我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.35,0:48:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.48,0:48:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿是哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.11,0:48:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骚屄里
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.77,0:48:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逼里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.38,0:48:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找你女儿也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.51,0:48:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.49,0:48:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要换你女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.81,0:49:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好张开哦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.09,0:49:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面真热乎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.69,0:49:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.59,0:49:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咋回事
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.88,0:49:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.57,0:49:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开心又惬意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.79,0:49:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表情挺不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.00,0:49:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该用嘴尝尝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.73,0:49:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.62,0:49:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,口交是很舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.58,0:49:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.91,0:49:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃鸡给女儿看看
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.52,0:49:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好教教女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.29,0:49:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看清楚妈妈怎么做的了吗 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.68,0:49:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舌头动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.64,0:49:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.36,0:49:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴在你妈逼里进进出出的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.39,0:50:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠近点儿看
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.06,0:50:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.15,0:50:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 换人了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.36,0:50:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.48,0:50:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.97,0:50:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看的兴奋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.16,0:50:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈被怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.84,0:50:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈被轮奸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.70,0:50:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃啊 鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.20,0:50:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被大家轮奸了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.89,0:50:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.51,0:50:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说“妈妈被轮奸了”
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.12,0:50:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对你妈说
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.46,0:50:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.18,0:50:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被轮奸了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.16,0:50:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.45,0:50:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个乖女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.25,0:51:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴有的是 想吃就吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.52,0:51:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 喜欢吃鸡巴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.14,0:51:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.27,0:51:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,边吃边回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.46,0:51:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.96,0:51:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃着陌生男人的鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.36,0:51:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还被操兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.77,0:51:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续操
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.52,0:51:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.18,0:51:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴口感好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.72,0:51:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.90,0:51:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉女儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.77,0:51:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超喜欢鸡巴对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.97,0:51:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.84,0:51:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈说超喜欢鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.09,0:51:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过来些
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.41,0:51:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看看你妈怎么吃鸡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.38,0:51:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说“妈妈 请让我看您吃鸡”
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.08,0:51:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.86,0:52:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说“妈妈 请让我看您吃鸡”
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.99,0:52:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不说你知道会怎样把
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.22,0:52:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.25,0:52:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.05,0:52:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让我看您吃鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.20,0:52:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 女儿都亲口说了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.62,0:52:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.51,0:52:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.67,0:52:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.20,0:52:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看好
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.20,0:52:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主动动起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.98,0:52:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.22,0:52:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话你懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.08,0:52:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈在努力挥腰啊 给她加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.07,0:52:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捏捏看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.94,0:52:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.91,0:52:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女儿也被鸡巴包围了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.03,0:52:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.51,0:52:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续吃
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.88,0:52:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你女儿都快把我撸射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.40,0:53:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你妈怎么吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.04,0:53:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.76,0:53:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.42,0:53:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.54,0:53:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你揉个够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.47,0:53:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.58,0:53:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛睁开
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.81,0:53:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.80,0:53:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴张着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.67,0:53:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.23,0:53:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃得真香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.71,0:53:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.62,0:54:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吧 这根火腿肠
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.71,0:54:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 在看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.48,0:54:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈应该很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.56,0:54:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不想体验妈妈有多舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.36,0:54:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去帮个忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.24,0:54:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.75,0:54:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.43,0:54:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.96,0:54:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在操你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.33,0:54:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.32,0:54:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.42,0:54:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被轮奸正爽着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.94,0:54:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.03,0:55:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.57,0:55:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让女儿看看
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.18,0:55:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.61,0:55:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被轮奸
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.77,0:55:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.53,0:55:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.34,0:55:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迫不及待想被操了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.37,0:55:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女儿看着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.17,0:55:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有鸡巴都还闲着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.99,0:55:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴还闲着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.62,0:55:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 看着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.54,0:56:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 让大家轮奸你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.51,0:56:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也请多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.02,0:56:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.40,0:56:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 多给力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.91,0:56:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看清楚你妈是怎么被别人操的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.45,0:56:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.43,0:56:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你妈把脸洗干净哦 看好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.35,0:56:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.79,0:56:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.32,0:56:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脸洗干净了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.65,0:57:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来看清楚些
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.68,0:57:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.50,0:57:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.54,0:57:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.62,0:57:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.19,0:57:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再近些
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.50,0:57:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.77,0:57:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.24,0:57:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.96,0:57:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看好
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.70,0:58:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看你妈的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.22,0:58:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.16,0:58:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈脸上沾着啥 说
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.38,0:58:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.66,0:58:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.89,0:58:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是精液啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.01,0:58:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说“妈妈脸上全是精液”
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.47,0:58:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.39,0:58:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 脸上全是精液
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.70,0:58:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.43,0:58:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来该 往你妈逼里射了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.69,0:58:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.98,0:58:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精液全给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.63,0:58:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要射进去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.91,0:58:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.23,0:59:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黏黏的出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.09,0:59:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.07,0:59:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才教过你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.60,0:59:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.80,0:59:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.85,0:59:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精液
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.29,0:59:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来该我了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.50,0:59:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别怕
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.93,1:00:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要射进去
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.15,1:00:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能怀上孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.37,1:00:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们生孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.07,1:00:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.07,1:00:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记住了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.64,1:00:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是弟弟还是妹妹呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.28,1:00:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你们 停下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.92,1:00:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈就是这样才能生下你的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.36,1:00:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且射进去很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.19,1:00:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.00,1:00:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.23,1:00:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.40,1:00:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又要射进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.41,1:00:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.36,1:00:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.97,1:00:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好品味吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.65,1:00:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.20,1:00:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了 射了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.54,1:01:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后还是射了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.95,1:01:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.10,1:01:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射完后必须这样弄干净哦 小姑娘学会了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.31,1:02:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射爽了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.31,1:02:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人妻的身体就是有玩头啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.24,1:02:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.31,1:02:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.63,1:02:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.11,1:02:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.83,1:02:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.00,1:03:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.20,1:03:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上床吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.62,1:03:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.00,1:03:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你用身体亲身实践吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.96,1:03:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.15,1:03:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.39,1:03:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你放过那孩子吧 她还小啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.74,1:03:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.81,1:03:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.09,1:03:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让完事的夫人消失吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.85,1:03:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.23,1:03:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要杀我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.02,1:04:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会听话
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.79,1:04:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再杀人了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.50,1:04:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是 藤泽步美
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.37,1:04:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(362,44)}（笑一个！接下来 我将开始第一次做爱）
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.79,1:05:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.67,1:05:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.91,1:05:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始第一次做爱
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.47,1:05:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是女儿的首次体验啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.27,1:05:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.90,1:05:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要好好记录下来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.33,1:06:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会让鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.03,1:06:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立起来的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.56,1:06:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,握住
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.72,1:06:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好握住
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.22,1:06:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手动起来
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.89,1:07:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.81,1:07:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.46,1:07:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硬邦邦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.00,1:07:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好粗哦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.10,1:07:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.78,1:07:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.65,1:07:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是干什么
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.90,1:07:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.99,1:07:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.87,1:07:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没做过这种事
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.81,1:08:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.51,1:08:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.26,1:08:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我牢牢衔在嘴里
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.58,1:08:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不听话你知道会怎么样吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.23,1:08:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎么做吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.29,1:08:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.17,1:08:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为啥要吐啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.86,1:09:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能认真点儿啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.50,1:09:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道怎么做了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.75,1:09:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃啊 主动点
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.48,1:09:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.26,1:10:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.60,1:10:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再激烈一些
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.73,1:10:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.60,1:10:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃进去啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.22,1:10:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你妈死活了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.08,1:10:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再进去些
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.34,1:11:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁说可以吐出来的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.21,1:11:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然那么多哈喇子
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.65,1:11:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看这儿
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.69,1:11:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,读这个
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.64,1:11:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,读
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.32,1:11:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看这边儿
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.53,1:11:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑一个
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.04,1:12:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请看
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.54,1:12:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这个
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.14,1:12:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.64,1:12:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合体的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.85,1:12:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骚屄吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.74,1:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.62,1:12:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.50,1:13:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在墨迹啥啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.77,1:13:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.94,1:13:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.16,1:13:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不听话
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.65,1:13:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈就会
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.99,1:13:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻利地脱掉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.49,1:14:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.11,1:14:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.38,1:14:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全力张开吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.43,1:14:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.99,1:14:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说 全力张开 啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.64,1:14:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把主题读出来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.55,1:14:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑一个
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.80,1:14:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都写在上面哦
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.62,1:14:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,读出来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.88,1:14:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.72,1:14:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.34,1:14:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生下
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.43,1:15:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.08,1:15:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.94,1:15:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.09,1:15:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,处女
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.36,1:15:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将被
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.57,1:15:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这根
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.79,1:15:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.07,1:15:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夺走
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.81,1:15:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.63,1:15:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见证
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.31,1:15:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.53,1:15:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为大人的瞬间吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.72,1:16:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发育成熟了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.28,1:16:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫你不准放开鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.02,1:16:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我看仔细些
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.46,1:17:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.15,1:17:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.42,1:17:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.62,1:17:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来个胜利手势
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.06,1:17:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何 舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.15,1:17:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你女儿似乎很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.84,1:18:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骚屄被别人看着
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.84,1:18:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.84,1:18:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.87,1:18:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硬了没有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.28,1:18:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不满足对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.66,1:18:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.99,1:19:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个瞬间将永远保留哦
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.88,1:19:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺积极的嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.10,1:19:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你插个爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.78,1:20:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你插个够哦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.40,1:20:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.98,1:20:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.33,1:20:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全就是大人了嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.07,1:20:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我彻底
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.06,1:20:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破掉你的处吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.02,1:20:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跨上来
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.78,1:21:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看哦
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.98,1:21:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这根
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.41,1:21:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.32,1:21:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对步美来说
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.67,1:21:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许太大了点
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.56,1:21:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我会努力
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.66,1:21:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一口气
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.90,1:21:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃到
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.19,1:21:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根部去的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.16,1:21:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.37,1:22:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我将
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.50,1:22:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这根鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.78,1:22:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插进
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.71,1:22:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骚屄里
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.46,1:22:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.86,1:22:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.78,1:22:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的第一次
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.83,1:22:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.82,1:22:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.76,1:22:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.07,1:22:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快插进去啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.39,1:22:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.34,1:22:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听话
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.22,1:23:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有下次了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.86,1:23:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.37,1:23:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 看好了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.47,1:23:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.57,1:23:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被破处
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.70,1:24:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才一半哦
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.59,1:24:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个插进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.80,1:24:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的插进去了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.64,1:24:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厉害啊 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.53,1:25:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.88,1:25:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成女人的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.58,1:25:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.12,1:25:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 上镜吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.18,1:25:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.01,1:25:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,处女膜
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.95,1:25:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.90,1:25:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.67,1:25:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贯穿 了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.51,1:25:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下子
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.83,1:25:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.94,1:25:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成大人了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.75,1:25:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.82,1:26:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.44,1:26:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在拔出来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.68,1:26:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真插进去了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.15,1:26:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.96,1:26:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始不间断骑乘位吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.15,1:26:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是敢中途停下
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.65,1:26:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就杀了你妈哦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.35,1:26:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好屁眼儿
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.75,1:26:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 笑一个啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.41,1:27:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈不知会怎么样哦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.79,1:27:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.10,1:27:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是奖励哦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.16,1:27:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑一个看看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.05,1:27:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.57,1:27:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了像妈妈一样
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.57,1:27:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶子变得大大的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.53,1:27:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你使劲揉揉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.78,1:28:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.86,1:28:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.77,1:28:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.86,1:28:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.65,1:28:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.05,1:28:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这呻吟真好听啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.29,1:29:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的屁屁
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.40,1:29:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我使劲操操吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.34,1:30:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.01,1:30:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天虽说是第一次
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.94,1:30:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全给你射进去哦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.15,1:30:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都射给你哦
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.44,1:31:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.62,1:31:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超爽
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.98,1:31:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被狠狠榨出去了的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.24,1:31:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后的场景了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.84,1:31:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.44,1:31:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是失败就再来一发哦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.35,1:32:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.45,1:32:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.85,1:32:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是第一次做爱
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.73,1:32:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却被
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.06,1:32:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射进了好多的精液
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.83,1:32:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是怀孕了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.65,1:32:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该能像妈妈一样
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.05,1:32:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.61,1:33:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大胸
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.55,1:33:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的 吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.87,1:33:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你细心抚养的女儿第一次榨出了精液啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.62,1:33:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好品尝吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.08,1:34:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.85,1:34:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.85,1:34:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.04,1:34:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都到晚饭时间了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.87,1:35:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.08,1:35:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.40,1:35:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在呢
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.86,1:35:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.10,1:35:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.10,1:35:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.54,1:35:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.08,1:36:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我好好榨出去
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.19,1:36:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欲罢不能啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.72,1:36:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怀上老子的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.43,1:36:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到个有意思的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.84,1:37:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.71,1:37:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.06,1:37:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛放开啊 吃啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.58,1:37:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不想去爸爸那边吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.11,1:37:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.78,1:37:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那首先 做自我介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.02,1:37:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.14,1:37:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开口啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.34,1:37:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫 藤泽舞
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.21,1:37:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.92,1:37:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道小婴儿是怎么怀上的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.42,1:37:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那正好
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.49,1:37:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.34,1:37:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.16,1:37:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会现场演示
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.46,1:38:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.47,1:38:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请放过小舞吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.55,1:38:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.79,1:38:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前从没见过吗
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.66,1:38:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快撸撸看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.03,1:38:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撸一撸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.12,1:38:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.41,1:38:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捏吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.36,1:38:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捏啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.94,1:38:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好捏啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.93,1:38:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.77,1:38:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墨迹个屁啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.20,1:38:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.97,1:38:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你们放过她
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.10,1:38:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人快教教你女儿吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.58,1:38:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不教教女儿怎么做吗
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.04,1:39:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是第一次对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.11,1:39:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一撸就硬对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.84,1:39:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.53,1:39:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这时要让男人爽起来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.31,1:39:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变坚挺了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.84,1:39:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.23,1:39:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要想怀上孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.18,1:39:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.70,1:39:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是靠手来撸
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.04,1:39:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要靠小舞的骚屄来撸啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.13,1:39:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.41,1:39:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这你身上长着的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.44,1:39:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们 不要
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.86,1:39:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.41,1:39:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用姐姐的逼
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.83,1:39:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实操一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.98,1:40:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.75,1:40:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实点 想让妈妈去死吗
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.24,1:40:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要一口气捅进去哦
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.43,1:40:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵啥吵
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.47,1:40:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想再做爱了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.10,1:40:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.91,1:40:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻利点
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.88,1:40:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻利点 快
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.22,1:40:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美 对不起\N快
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.14,1:40:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想去陪爸爸了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.46,1:40:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我快没耐心了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.73,1:40:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.04,1:40:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞是第一次见识这个吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.05,1:41:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腰别停啊
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.87,1:41:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞也加油撸啊
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.45,1:41:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快看姐姐是怎么做的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.21,1:41:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.68,1:41:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 教教你女儿吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.92,1:41:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教教吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.47,1:41:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.00,1:42:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用小脸蛋儿接住吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.48,1:42:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是精液
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.59,1:42:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准洒了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.10,1:42:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面都是小婴儿哦 你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.97,1:42:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也再加把劲
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.87,1:42:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教教妹妹
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.88,1:43:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐要做好示范啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.47,1:43:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要射啦
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.39,1:43:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.41,1:43:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.97,1:43:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都谁给你姐姐哦
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.30,1:43:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.99,1:43:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.12,1:43:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.43,1:43:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.92,1:43:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐示范的不错吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.88,1:43:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.96,1:44:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快点清理的话
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.72,1:44:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子就怀上了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.17,1:44:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐受精完毕
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.12,1:44:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.57,1:44:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要怀上婴儿了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.98,1:44:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想怀孕
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.06,1:44:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许是个女孩哦
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.94,1:44:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 该轮到小舞了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.95,1:44:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.67,1:44:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少请你们放过这孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.11,1:44:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是最嫩的
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.23,1:45:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱掉
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.49,1:45:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清晰可见啊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.54,1:45:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,颜色看起来挺嫩啊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.47,1:45:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际操着爽不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.41,1:45:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.12,1:45:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.93,1:45:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.97,1:46:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.40,1:46:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.66,1:46:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴应有尽有啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.35,1:46:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对够吃哦
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.09,1:46:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很硬
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.10,1:46:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看这边 舔吗
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.53,1:46:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个会贯穿你哦
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.79,1:46:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想吃鸡吗
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.57,1:46:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就直接挨操吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.97,1:46:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看好哦
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.90,1:47:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么紧啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.52,1:47:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事儿
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.25,1:47:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会教你怎么插进去
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.11,1:47:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进去了\N龟头进去了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.73,1:47:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们见证小舞成为大人吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.77,1:47:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被操了有何感想啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.81,1:47:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被操了有何感想啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.17,1:47:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.23,1:47:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一口气捅进去哦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.62,1:47:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预 备
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.83,1:47:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好极了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.04,1:47:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个插进去啦 不愧是夫人的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.64,1:47:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛逼哦
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.61,1:48:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要拔掉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.93,1:48:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.43,1:48:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 恭喜被破处
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.38,1:48:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜哦\N和你同学比我是最大的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.42,1:48:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在一口气拔掉哦
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.70,1:48:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.14,1:48:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流血了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.27,1:48:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这啥啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.93,1:48:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜破处
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.81,1:48:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.71,1:49:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.55,1:49:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这还只是开始哦
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.57,1:49:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要狠狠操你哦
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.94,1:49:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.34,1:49:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐上来
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.86,1:49:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越里面越好
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.92,1:49:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.91,1:49:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.34,1:49:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽量露出来
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.93,1:49:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真磨蹭 再里面去点儿
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.47,1:50:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错 意外的不错啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.65,1:50:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激烈点儿
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.41,1:50:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也渐渐舒服起来了
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.16,1:50:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腰的动作不够激烈
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.38,1:50:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在让骚屄多热热身
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.95,1:50:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要使劲操你哦
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.33,1:51:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁眼儿拿过来
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.53,1:51:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看清楚了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.75,1:52:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 爽
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.79,1:52:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.75,1:52:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 对不起\N你妹的逼挺紧啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.93,1:52:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不输给姐姐和妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.47,1:52:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个女儿都很紧啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.84,1:52:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人有个好女儿呢
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.62,1:52:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.04,1:52:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你比你妈妈操起来还爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.53,1:53:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别吵
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.94,1:53:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我看好了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.82,1:53:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.57,1:53:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.64,1:53:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看好
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.21,1:53:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.03,1:53:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小逼在发抖啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.18,1:54:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快娇喘看看
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.34,1:54:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看清楚了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.15,1:54:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.14,1:54:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就射给你哦
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.11,1:55:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点怀上孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.81,1:55:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘是在娇喘吗
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.34,1:55:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好受精准备了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.60,1:55:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接住哦
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.12,1:55:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逼夹得太紧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.23,1:55:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴招架不住哦
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.15,1:55:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射精预备
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.43,1:56:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们 已经够了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.29,1:56:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了不少哦
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.14,1:57:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.07,1:57:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射的够多啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.73,1:57:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怀孕没跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.09,1:57:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.40,1:57:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.70,1:57:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这量够大啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:32.15,1:57:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时怀孕的节奏啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:37.92,1:57:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪个都被射了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.39,1:57:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 又流出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.80,1:57:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还远没有结束哦
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.56,1:57:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们母女要尽力满足大伙儿
